OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780319468
OL,3,CLast-ditch talks aim to avert London
OL,4,CTube strikes
OL,6,FThe industrial action is in response
OL,7,Fto issues including a new working week
OL,8,Fwhich the RMT has said its members do
OL,9,Fnot agree with.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "Our members have
OL,12,Fraised serious concerns around
OL,13,Ffatigue, longer shifts, reduced
OL,14,Fflexibility and the impact these
OL,15,Fproposals could have in a safety-
OL,16,Fcritical role."
OL,18,FHowever, the drivers' union Aslef has
OL,19,Faccepted the new arrangements.
OL,26,@sD@VOUxD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
