OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1780319468
OL,3,CLast-ditch talks aim to avert London
OL,4,CTube strikes
OL,6,FAslef says the voluntary compressed
OL,7,Ffour-day week gives participating
OL,8,Fstaff an extra 35 days off a year in
OL,9,Freturn for some "fairly minor changes
OL,10,Fto working conditions".
OL,12,FBut a union source said Tube drivers
OL,13,Fhad "very real" concerns about
OL,14,Fspending longer hours in the driver
OL,15,Fcab, "becoming more fatigued, losing
OL,16,Fflexibility around their shifts and
OL,17,Fthe impact that could have on a role
OL,18,Fwhere safety has to come first."
OL,26,@qD@QOUrD@VO]uD@EOUuD@OO]zD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
