OL,3,CLast-ditch talks aim to avert London
OL,4,CTube strikes
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FTfL has said it would never compromise
OL,12,Fsafety, adding that the new shift
OL,13,Fsystem was voluntary.
OL,15,FIt hopes to run at least half of Tube
OL,16,Fservices, but the Circle and
OL,17,FPiccadilly lines will not run, nor
OL,18,Fwill the Metropolitan line between
OL,19,FBaker Street and Aldgate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
